articles.title: Prince George's animated reactions steal the show at Euro 2020 final - CTV News
articles.description: England's first trip to the European Championship finals didn’t exactly go as planned after losing to Italy during the penalty shootout. But for many on the internet, it was the animated reactions of Prince George that stole the show.
